# Loose/unsorted image files staged in assets/ should NOT be auto-committed.
# Only files explicitly wired into a page get added by name (git add assets/<name>).
# This prevents accidental publishing of copyrighted or unsorted photos via
# `git add -A` (which happened once with film posters).
assets/*.tmp
assets/_unsorted/
# Camera-named files are working uploads until renamed to a page slot:
assets/IMG_*.jpg
assets/IMG_*.JPG
assets/20??????_*.jpg
